# Architecture

**Canonical source:** [`docs/BLUEPRINT.md`](../../docs/BLUEPRINT.md)

When editing `src/` or `tests/`:

- Flat `tests/{feature}.spec.ts` — tags in titles, not tier folders (see ADR-0002)
- Kebab-case filenames · PascalCase class names
- Specs import `@fixtures` — never `@playwright/test` directly
- Path aliases: `@fixtures`, `@pages/*`, `@data/*`, `@config/*`

Layer boundaries and full layout: [`docs/BLUEPRINT.md`](../../docs/BLUEPRINT.md).
